'''Watampone''' is a city in [[South Sulawesi]] and the capital of [[Bone Regency]]. Known colloquially as ''Bone'', it has a population of 81,629.<ref name="Berkmoes2010">{{cite book|author=Ryan Ver Berkmoes|title=Indonesia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4GMBFsaFNN4C&pg=PA670|accessdate=5 January 2013|date=1 January 2010|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74104-830-8|pages=670â€“}}</ref> It is also the birthplace of the [[List of Vice Presidents of Indonesia|10th]] and [[List of Vice Presidents of Indonesia|12th]] [[Vice President of the Republic of Indonesia]] [[Jusuf Kalla]].

